query:
INSERT INTO propertyImages (propertyId, imageUrl) 
SELECT p.id, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502672260266-1c1ef2d93688?w=800&h=600&fit=crop' as imageUrl
FROM properties p
WHERE p.id NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT propertyId FROM propertyImages);
